[start section id="20102"]

Rectal cancer.

[end section id="20102"]

[start section id="20103"]

This is a 72-year-old woman whom I had seen previously with a very low rectal cancer which basically started in her anal canal.  She underwent chemoradiation therapy which she tolerated well.  Restaging has not shown any progression of the disease.  She is now here in preparation for surgery.

[end section id="20103"]


